    <h1>Review Sentiment</h1>
    <p class="description">The qualitative tone of customer reviews as analyzed by Google's NLP systems. Goes beyond star ratings — <strong>the words customers use directly influence local search rankings</strong> and the quotes Google displays in search results.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
